## Elevation (light mode shadows — layered low alpha)
  --shadow-sm: 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.04), 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
  --shadow-md: 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.06), 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.04), 0 8px 16px -4px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
  --shadow-lg: 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.06), 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.04), 0 12px 24px -8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);

In dark mode, set all shadow values to `none` and rely on --border instead.

## Accent usage (the part previous passes got wrong)
Use --accent confidently. It MUST be visibly present above the fold:
  - "Live" pill: bg --bg-accent, text --accent — visibly blue, not subtle
  - Pattern Status sidebar active row: 6px filled circle in --accent
  - Demo toggle active state: bg --accent, white knob
  - Focus rings everywhere: 2px solid --accent, offset 2px

NEVER use --accent for body links (those use --text underline) or full-section backgrounds.

## Banned characters in copy
  - Em-dashes (—) → replace with period + new sentence, OR a colon
  - Right arrows (→) in body copy → remove
  - Middle dots (·) → footer meta line only

## Banned hedge words (search and remove)
thoughtfully, carefully, seamlessly, robust, leverage, intuitive, delightful, powerful, elegant, modern, beautifully

## Density rules
- Max content width: 1120px
- Section vertical padding: 120px desktop, 80px mobile
- Card padding: 28px
- Card grid gap: 20px
- Cards: bg-elevated, radius 12px, box-shadow var(--shadow-sm), no border (the shadow ring IS the border)
- Live card hover: shadow-md + translate-y -2px, transition 200ms ease-out